{
  "id": "adv_event_2401_01_02",
  "title": "芽衣の猫探し",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一方その頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Meanwhile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.1666667047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "沙季が大掃除を始めてすぐ、芽衣は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shortly after Saki started cleaning‚ Mei was――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.1666667047,
      "endTime": 3.1200001717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "大掃除を手伝うって、つい言っちゃったけど\n掃除って何をすればいいんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I blurted out that I'd help with the cleaning‚\nbut what am I supposed to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0000002702,
      "endTime": 12.0128799279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえず、散らかってる雑誌を片付けようかな\n適当に棚に押し込んでおけばいいよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I’ll start by putting away these scattered magazines.\nI can just shove them on the shelf‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2078459422,
      "endTime": 19.8845577876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "この漫画はこっちの棚に入れて……あれ？\n棚の下に何か落ちてる。これは……ペンダント？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll put this comic on this shelf… Hmm?\nSomething fell under the shelf. Is this… a pendant?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0795238018,
      "endTime": 33.1939454555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "誰かの忘れ物かな？　こういうのは目立つ所に置いて\nおいた方がいいよね？　目立つ所、目立つ所……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if someone forgot this? it would be better\nto put it somewhere visible… visible‚ visible…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3889114697,
      "endTime": 45.324626000600006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　この招き猫の首にペンダントをかけて……\nわぁ、招き猫にゃん可愛い～。すっごく目立ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gotcha! I’ll hang the pendant on the neck of this maneki-neko…\nWow‚ maneki-neko-nyan‚ you are so cute~. It really stands out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5195920149,
      "endTime": 57.458843724000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "……えっと、芽衣は何をやってたんだっけ？\nそうそう、大掃除してて、漫画を棚に入れようと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ what was I doing again?\nOh yeah‚ I was cleaning and trying to put the comic on the shelf…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6538097381,
      "endTime": 67.4125394821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、この漫画、よく見たら……\n前から読みたかったやつだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ when I look closely at this manga…\nIt’s the one I’ve been wanting to read!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6075054963,
      "endTime": 73.7677097161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――小一時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――About an hour later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.6626784007,
      "endTime": 75.7626784007,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1299.9994912999996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……芽衣ちゃん。どうしてこたつに入って\n漫画を読んでいるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mei-chan. Why are you in the kotatsu\nreading comics?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0293465932,
      "endTime": 82.0497774442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん！\nこの漫画の続き、どこにあるか知らない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan!\nDo you know where the next volume of this manga is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2626799266,
      "endTime": 86.66451660800001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "（って、こんな感じで大掃除は全然進まなくて）\n（この後も沙季ちゃんとDVDを見たりして……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Like this‚ the big cleaning hasn’t progressed at all.）\n（And after that‚ I watched a DVD with Saki-chan…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0594795704,
      "endTime": 95.8707272054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "むにゃむにゃ……\n……ん？　あれ？　ここは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mumble mumble…\n…Hmm? Huh? Where…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1323588689,
      "endTime": 106.90975106559999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、そっか\nDVD見ながら寝ちゃったんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ that’s right.\nI fell asleep while watching the DVD…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1047170799,
      "endTime": 111.9822455566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "すー……すー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zzz… Zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1772115708,
      "endTime": 122.0772111893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん、気持ち良さそうな顔で寝てるけど\n疲れてたのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan’s sleeping with such a peaceful look on her face.\nMaybe she was tired?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3105413437,
      "endTime": 129.553647995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのためにいつも頑張ってくれてるもんね……\nありがとう、沙季ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s always working so hard for Moon Tempest…\nThank you‚ Saki-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7486140092,
      "endTime": 135.9904961427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ん……芽衣ちゃんも……\nいつも、ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Mei-chan you too…\n…Thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.185462157,
      "endTime": 145.9397479694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～、寝言でお礼言われちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe~‚ she thanked me in her sleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.0854601224,
      "endTime": 150.06729691820001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが居眠りしちゃったのは\n芽衣と一緒にいると居心地いいって思ってくれたから？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that Saki-chan fell asleep\nbecause she feels comfortable around me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2622751396,
      "endTime": 157.29320499110003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "だとしたら……ちょっと嬉しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If so… I’m a little happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4881710053,
      "endTime": 161.2042934418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、大掃除やるぞ～。沙季ちゃんが寝てる間に\n部屋をピカピカにして、起きた時に驚かせちゃうよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I’m going to clean~. I’ll make the room sparkling clean while Saki-chan’s asleep‚\nand surprise her when she wakes up~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.499259456,
      "endTime": 173.2309601625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "どの部屋からお掃除しようかな\n……あれ？　なんだろう、このカゴ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which room should I clean first?\n…Huh? What’s this basket?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.4259261768,
      "endTime": 180.4282844226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "こんな所にカゴなんて置いてあったっけ？\n中に何が入ってるんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was there a basket here?\nI wonder what’s inside…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.6232504368,
      "endTime": 186.9679214955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "猫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Cat",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃ～ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meow~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.1628875097,
      "endTime": 188.7562249144,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "わあああっ！　猫ちゃんだ～！　可愛い～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaaah! It’s a kitty! So cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.9628915787,
      "endTime": 194.359943676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "猫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Cat",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.5549096902,
      "endTime": 195.6815570314,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_02-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、カゴの外に出ちゃダメだよ\nわわっ、廊下を走り回っちゃダメ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you can’t go outside the basket.\nOh no‚ don’t run around in the hallway~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.8882236957,
      "endTime": 203.18527588839999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "猫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Cat",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃあっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.3802419026,
      "endTime": 204.3802418907,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
